	dprr:hasNoteText "Legatus (Liv. Per. 76). After successes in Lucania, he fell during the siege of an enemy camp (Liv. Per. 76; Flor. 2.6.13, against the Marsi; Oros. 5.18.25, with praenomen C.). See 101, Quaestors." ;
